name: Armaill
desc: A strange warrior who manipulates three deadly blades with both hands and his tail.

name: 30,000-Year White Turtle
desc: A huge turtle that has existed for more than 30,000 years.

name: 7 Colored Fish
desc: A rare rainbow fish that has never been caught by mortal man.

name: Absolute King - Megaplunder
desc: ''The king of dinosaurs that rules over the Earth. Its mighty roar makes its foes tremble in fear!''

name: Abyss Flower
desc: A rarely seen flower that blossoms quietly on the edge of darkness.

name: Acid Crawler
desc: A giant caterpillar that secretes an acid mist that melts anything.

name: Acrobat Monkey
desc: An autonomous monkey type robot which was developed with cutting-edge technology. It moves very acrobatically.

name: Air Eater
desc: A monster that feeds on oxygen, suffocating any who stand near.

name: Aitsu
desc: He seems to be very unreliable, but he might have incredible potential.

name: Akakieisu
desc: A sorcerer who utters spells that render monsters unconscious.

name: Akihiron
desc: This strange creature hides in the deep, dark corners of the seven seas.

name: Alexandrite Dragon
desc: Many of the czars' lost jewels can be found in the scales of this priceless dragon. Its creator remains a mystery, along with how they acquired the imperial treasures. But whosoever finds this dragon has hit the jackpot... whether they know it or not.

name: Alien Shocktrooper
desc: The Aliens have used a mysterious biological substance to create a supreme race of soldiers. They do not have the natural powers of the other Aliens, but can make stunning physical attacks.

name: Alinsection
desc: A stag beetle with a saw-like head and arms.

name: Alligator's Sword
desc: ey, dis mighty lissard man can swing his sword so fast, dat it's more dan da speed a sound!

name: Ally of Justice Clausolas
desc: A mighty monster in Mist Valley, and the ultimate weapon designed from Claiomh Solais. Its surprise attacks from above baffle invaders.

name: Alpha The Magnet Warrior
desc: ''Alpha, Beta, and Gamma meld as one to form a powerful monster.''

name: Amazon of the Seas
desc: A mermaid who serves as a herald to the Ocean Lord. She protects the sacred domain of Atlantis.

name: Amphibian Beast
desc: On land or in the sea, the speed of this monster is unmatchable.

name: Ancient Brain
desc: A fallen fairy that is powerful in the dark.

name: Ancient Elf
desc: This elf is rumored to have lived for thousands of years. He leads an army of spirits against his enemies.

name: Ancient Jar
desc: A very fragile jar that contains something ancient and dangerous.

name: Ancient Lizard Warrior
desc: Before the dawn of man, this lizard warrior ruled supreme.

name: Ancient One of the Deep Forest
desc: This creature adopts the form of a white goat living in the forest, but is actually a Forest Elder.

name: Ancient Sorcerer
desc: Armed with an array of magic wands, this creature is capable of multiple attacks.

name: Ancient Tool
desc: A destructive machine discovered in the Ruins of the Ancients.

name: Ancient Tree of Enlightenment
desc: This ancient arbor uses its extensive knowledge to avoid the damage of enemy attacks.

name: Anotherverse Dragon
desc: ''This secretive dragon has conquered many dimensions, but can only be seen by the champion of time.''

name: Anotherverse Gluttonia
desc: ''A massive, malevolent monstrosity, devourer of diverse dimensions, who molds multiple domains where only the mightiest dare dwell.''

name: Ansatsu
desc: A silent and deadly warrior specializing in assassinations.

name: Anthrosaurus
desc: Dis man-like dinosawz gotta high I.Q., even tho he's lackin' in da strength depawtment. (Kinda like yooz, if ya had a high I.Q.! Nyaah!)

name: Aqua Madoor
desc: A wizard of the waters that conjures a liquid wall to crush any enemies that oppose him.

name: Aqua Snake
desc: This monster hypnotizes an opponent with the ball on its tail and draws them to a watery doom.

name: Archfiend Marmot of Nefariousness
desc: An air marmot that has a nefarious horn and wings. It attacks by throwing acorns.

name: Archfiend Mirror
desc: A wicked mirror that hypnotizes enemies, diverting attacks from their intended targets.

name: Archfiend Soldier
desc: An expert at battle who belongs to a crack diabolical unit. He's famous because he always gets the job done.

name: Arlownay
desc: A lady monster dwelling in a flower, she sprinkles the air with poisonous pollen.

name: Arma Knight
desc: An ammonite warrior that has protected the seas throughout history.

name: Armaill
desc: A strange warrior who manipulates three deadly blades with both hands and his tail.

name: Armored Lizard
desc: A lizard with a very tough hide and a vicious bite.

name: Armored Rat
desc: The fur on this monster rat is tough enough to repel swords.

name: Armored Starfish
desc: A bluish starfish with a solid hide capable of fending off attacks.

name: Armored Zombie
desc: This warrior blindly swings a deadly blade with devastating force.

name: Atlantean Pikeman
desc: The Great Ocean Lord, who reigns over the depths, is served by these lancers. Deep-sea creatures exist in fear of facing the stream of attacks their lances are capable of.

name: Axe Raider
desc: An axe-wielding monster of tremendous strength and agility.

name: B. Dragon Jungle King
desc: A jet-black dragon found in the deepest jungles who normally devours trees.

name: Baby Dragon
desc: Much more than just a child, this dragon is gifted with untapped power.

name: Baron of the Fiend Sword
desc: An aristocrat who wields a sword possessed by a malicious spirit that preys on the weak.

name: Barrel Lily
desc: This wicked flower attacks enemies with pollen projectiles.

name: Barrel Rock
desc: Shouldering a pair of machine guns, this monster is unstoppable.

name: Basic Insect
desc: Usually found traveling in swarms, this creature's ideal environment is the forest.

name: Bat
desc: A mechanical bat that drops blasts from its wings.

name: Battle Footballer
desc: A cyborg with high defense power. Originally it was invented for a football machine.

name: Battle Ox
desc: A monster with tremendous power, it destroys enemies with a swing of its axe.

name: Battle Steer
desc: A bull monster often found in the woods, it charges enemy monsters with a pair of deadly horns.

name: Battle Warrior
desc: A warrior that fights with his bare hands!!!

name: Beaked Snake
desc: This monster wraps itself around an opponent and pecks away with its huge beak.

name: Bean Soldier
desc: A plant-warrior that attacks with seeds and sword.

name: Beast of Talwar
desc:
Only the master of the sword among Fiend-Type monsters is permitted to hold the Talwar.


(This card is always treated as an "Archfiend" card.)

name: Beautiful Beast Trainer
desc: A rare female beast-master with a very dangerous whip.

name: Beautiful Headhuntress
desc: A vicious creature that has decapitated numerous enemy monsters.

name: Beaver Warrior
desc: What this creature lacks in size it makes up for in defense when battling in the prairie.

name: Beckoned by the World Chalice
desc: His battle with the Mekkstrosities never seems to end. Even when their forest was invaded by Mekkstrocious Insects, he stood his ground and inspired the other defenders around him.

name: Behegon
desc: With an enormous maw and massive teeth, this monstrosity is one dangerous and strange serpent from the deep.

name: Beta The Magnet Warrior
desc: ''Alpha, Beta, and Gamma meld as one to form a powerful monster.''

name: Big Insect
desc: A giant ant that dwells in the jungle, it is powerful whether attacking or defending.

name: Big Koala
desc: A species of huge Des Koala. He's meek, but people are afraid of him because he's very powerful.

name: Binding Chain
desc: The mystic links of this chain can rob enemies of their power.

name: Bio Plant
desc: A monster created from a major accident in an underground lab.

name: Bio-Mage
desc: A mysterious priest created as a result of the latest advances in biotechnology.

name: Bitron
desc: A new species found in electronic space. There's not much information on it.

name: Blackland Fire Dragon
desc: A dragon that dwells in the depths of darkness, its vulnerability lies in its poor eyesight.

name: Blade Skater
desc: An image of beauty on the ice, this gorgeous warrior rips her opponents into pieces with her stylish Accel Slicer attack.

name: Blazing Inpachi
desc: A wicked wooden spirit now burning in flames. Its fire attack is powerful, but it will soon be nothing but ashes.

name: Blocker
desc: Constructed from several components, this monster can launch them in a pincer attack.

name: Blue-Eyed Silver Zombie
desc: The beams from the eyes of this creature are said to turn enemies into zombies.

name: Blue-Eyes White Dragon
desc: This legendary dragon is a powerful engine of destruction. Virtually invincible, very few have faced this awesome creature and lived to tell the tale.

name: Blue-Winged Crown
desc: With hair shaped like a crown and a body encased in bluish white flames, this bird is a formidable sight.

name: Bokoichi the Freightening Car
desc: A freight car that is exclusively for Dekoichi. It can transport anything, but most cargo arrives broken.

name: Bolt Escargot
desc: After rendering an opponent immobile by spitting a sticky goo, this monster closes in for the attack.

name: Bolt Penguin
desc: With each arm forming an electric whip, this monster paralyzes its enemies with electric shocks.

name: Bone Mouse
desc: A mouse that has returned as a zombie to seek revenge on cats.

name: Boneheimer
desc: This monster wanders the seas, sucking dry any creatures it may encounter.

name: Boo Koo
desc: A book-like wizard with a wealth of magic written inside.

name: Bottom Dweller
desc: This is one sea creature whose wrath is something monsters fear to face.

name: Boulder Tortoise
desc: A stone turtle that is nearly indestructible.

name: Brave Scizzar
desc: Armed with a mass of scissors, this monster can clip an enemy into any desired shape and size.

name: Bunilla
desc: This rabbit's got a sweet tooth! He's on a quest for the world's sweetest carrot, and just wants to nibble carrots all day today, tomorrow, and the day after that!

name: Burglar
desc: A sly rat. He will come at you with his huge left claw.

name: Candle of Fate
desc: Decides the fate of an opponent when the candle on its fingertip burns out.

name: Celtic Guardian
desc: An elf who learned to wield a sword, he baffles enemies with lightning-swift attacks.

name: Chamberlain of the Six Samurai
desc: The Six Samurai are supported from the shadows by this silent and mysterious warrior. His past is unknown to them, but his countless scars are proof of his experience.

name: Change Slime
desc: A slime that can morph and adopt the shape and size of any monster it chooses.

name: Charcoal Inpachi
desc: A wicked wooden spirit that has burned out. The barbecue grilled with this charcoal is so awesome that everybody thinks it's priceless.

name: Chosen by the World Chalice
desc: Inspired by the World Hero legends he heard as a boy, this crusader adds a piece to his armor from every Mekkstrosity he destroys. He has set out on a quest from Fairy Lee to recover the Seven World Legacies and save their world.

name: Chu-Ske the Mouse Fighter
desc: A fiery mouse, travelling the world to become the strongest fighter in the world of mice. Be careful not to touch him, or you will get burned.

name: Clavkiys, the Magikey Skyblaster
desc:
''Everyone is full of possibilities. Everything you do, moving forwards, stopping, closing, opening, is all in your hands.
There are many doors in this world. To open them requires the Magic Key... 2 keys and 1 door... 2 wills and 1 body. Once the doors are opened, the worlds will be connected and the great power revealed.''

name: Claw Reacher
desc: Stretching arms and razor-sharp claws make this monster a formidable opponent.

name: Cloudian - Smoke Ball
desc: Smoke Balls are newly born Cloudians. They fear being alone, and would rather swing and sway in the sky with their friends.

name: Clown Zombie
desc: A clown revived by the powers of darkness. Its deadly dance has sent many monsters to their graves.

name: Corroding Shark
desc: A zombie shark that can deliver its lethal curse with a spell.

name: Cosmo Queen
desc: Queen of the galaxies and mistress of the stars.

name: Crawling Dragon
desc: This weakened dragon can no longer fly, but is still a deadly force to be reckoned with.

name: Crawling Dragon #2
desc: A powerful dragon with teeth that can grind almost anything to dust.

name: Crazy Fish
desc: A flying fish that attacks with its pointed head.

name: Crow Goblin
desc: A clever long-nosed goblin, he is a force to be reckoned with.

name: Crowned by the World Chalice
desc: With her magical staff, she can channel the living heart of her world to shield her people from the Mekk-Knights that have overrun it.

name: Curse of Dragon
desc: A wicked dragon that taps into dark forces to execute a powerful attack.

name: Curtain of the Dark Ones
desc: A curtain that a spellcaster made, it is said to raise a dark power.

name: Cyber Commander
desc: A strike force equipped with rocket launchers and bazookas.

name: Cyber Falcon
desc: A jet-powered hawk that travels at the speed of sound.

name: Cyber Soldier
desc: Guardian of the Machine Master, it crushes opposition by rolling over them.

name: Cyber Soldier of Darkworld
desc: A mechanical soldier that won't stop attacking until all life readings have been extinguished from its sensors.

name: Cyber-Tech Alligator
desc: Originally a pterodactyl, he was viciously attacked by a dragon. Using the newest technologies, his keeper saved him from near-fatal wounds and brought him back as a powerful Cyborg.

name: Cycroid
desc: The most lovable and friendly of all the Vehicroids. It can arm itself with training wheels!

name: D. Human
desc: Gifted with the power of dragons, this warrior wields a sword created from a dragon's fang.

name: D.D. Trainer
desc: A poor goblin that was sucked into a different dimension. However, he's doing his best with his new destiny.

name: Dancing Elf
desc: An elf that dances across the sky with wings of razor-sharp blades.

name: Dark Assailant
desc: Armed with the Psycho Sword, this sinister assassin rules the bad land.

name: Dark Bat
desc: Bats from the netherworld that use their hyper senses to detect their enemies.

name: Dark Blade
desc: They say he is a dragon-manipulating warrior from the dark world. His attack is tremendous, using his great swords with vicious power.

name: Dark Chimera
desc: A fire-breathing monster that dwells in the netherworld.

name: Dark Gray
desc: Entirely gray, this beast has rarely been seen by mortal eyes.

name: Dark King of the Abyss
desc: It's said that this King of the Netherworld once had the power to rule over the dark.

name: Dark Magician
desc: ''The ultimate wizard in terms of attack and defense.''

name: Dark Plant
desc: This mutant flower draws its power from pollutants and the dark forces.

name: Dark Prisoner
desc: This monster bends light to hide its image from the eyes of opponents.

name: Dark Rabbit
desc: He leaps up, down, and all around! Nobody can lay a hand on this funny bunny.

name: Dark Shade
desc: A crystal monster that unleashes a brilliant light to blind enemies.

name: Dark Titan of Terror
desc: A fiend said to dwell in the world of dreams, it attacks enemies in their sleep.

name: Dark Witch
desc: A popular creature in mythology that delivers fatal attacks with a sharp spear.

name: Darkfire Soldier #1
desc: An explosive expert from a special elite force.

name: Darkfire Soldier #2
desc: A warrior who gained immeasurable power from the heart of a volcano.

name: Darkworld Thorns
desc: A thorny plant found in the darklands that wraps itself around any unwary traveler.

name: Destroyer Golem
desc: A golem with a massive right hand for crushing its victims.

name: Dharma Cannon
desc: A monstrous creature whose body is lined with cannons that never miss their targets.

name: Dice Armadillo
desc: An armadillo monster that rolls up to form a dice-like shape.

name: Dig Beak
desc: This beast coils like a snake, and strikes quickly with its snapping beak.

name: Digitron
desc: A subspecies found in electronic space. There's little information on it.

name: Disk Magician
desc: This monster hides in a saucer and only appears when executing an attack.

name: Dissolverock
desc: A monster born in the lava pits, it generates intense heat that can melt away its enemies.

name: Divine Dragon Ragnarok
desc: A legendary dragon sent by the gods as their instrument. Legends say that if provoked, the whole world will sink beneath the sea.

name: Djinn the Watcher of the Wind
desc: This creature generates gale-force winds and tornadoes to blow its enemies away.

name: Dokuroizo the Grim Reaper
desc: A messenger of doom that steals a soul with a single blow.

name: Dokuroyaiba
desc: A boomerang with brains that will pursue a target to the ends of the earth.

name: Doll Monster Bear-Bear
desc:
''Even if we get damaged, it's okay.
Grandpa Demetto can patch us up!''

name: Doll Monster Miss Mdchen
desc:
''Welcome to our house!
Here I live with Cologne, Grandpa Demetto, and all the other dolls!''

name: Doma The Angel of Silence
desc: This fairy rules over the end of existence.

name: Doriado
desc: A spirit of the forest powered by the surrounding trees and wildlife.

name: Doron
desc: This monster splits in two and attacks from opposite sides.

name: Dorover
desc: This ugly monster emits a highly poisonous gas.

name: Dragon Statue
desc: A stone warrior with the heart of a dragon.

name: Dragon Zombie
desc: A dragon revived by sorcery. Its breath is highly corrosive.

name: Droll Bird
desc: This monster stuns its enemies with a massive beak and ear-piercing wails.

name: Drooling Lizard
desc: A blood-sucking snake in human form that attacks any living being that passes nearby.

name: Dunames Dark Witch
desc: Even when all odds are against this brave fairy, she will press onwards in battle and never retreat.

name: Dungeon Worm
desc: Hidden under the floors of a labyrinth, it swallows any who pass above.

name: Earthbound Spirit
desc: A vengeful creature formed by the spirits of fallen warriors, it drags any who dare approach it into the deepest bowels of the earth.

name: Eldeen
desc: The cane of this monster is the source of many powerful spells.

name: Elemental HERO Avian
desc: A winged Elemental HERO who wheels through the sky and manipulates the wind. His signature move, Featherbreak, gives villainy a blow from sky-high.

name: Elemental HERO Burstinatrix
desc: A flame manipulator who was the first Elemental HERO woman. Her Burstfire burns away villainy.

name: Elemental HERO Clayman
desc: An Elemental HERO with a clay body built-to-last. He'll preserve his Elemental HERO colleagues at any cost.

name: Elemental HERO Sparkman
desc: An Elemental HERO and a warrior of light who proficiently wields many kinds of armaments. His Static Shockwave cuts off the path of villainy.

name: Embryonic Beast
desc: An imperfect monster with a belly vortex that sucks in opponents of any size.

name: Emperor of the Land and Sea
desc: A reptilian monster that sprays fire in every direction.

name: Empress Mantis
desc: Queen of an army of giant mantises whose command moves legions.

name: Enchanting Mermaid
desc: A beautiful mermaid that lures voyagers to a watery grave.

name: Evilswarm Heliotrope
desc: .ytilaer a maerd rieht ekam thgim yeht taht os ydob a rof gninraey ,sluos mrawsleetS gniregnil fo sthguoht eht era esehT "!etanimretxE !etacidarE !etanimilE"

name: Eyearmor
desc: This warrior transforms into various creatures to confuse enemies in battle.

name: Fairy Dragon
desc: This beautiful Dragon spirit harbors hidden strength.

name: Fairy of the Fountain
desc: This fairy protects a fountain from any who seek to muddy its waters.

name: Fairy's Gift
desc: This flying monster is known for delivering happiness to all.

name: Fairywitch
desc: Though destined to be a fairy, this creature chose the way of the witch instead.

name: Faith Bird
desc: This long-tailed bird blinds its enemies with mystical light.

name: Feral Imp
desc: A playful little fiend that lurks in the dark, waiting to attack an unwary enemy.

name: Fiend Kraken
desc: A giant squid that drags its enemies to a watery grave.

name: Fiend Reflection #1
desc: This monster can draw its enemies into a mirror world that renders them helpless.

name: Fiend Reflection #2
desc: A bird-beast that summons reinforcements with a hand mirror.

name: Fiend Scorpion
desc: A huge scorpion inhabited by the soul of a fiend. Usually it holds back, but has untapped potential.

name: Fiend Sword
desc: Whoever resists the curse of this blade will gain untold power.

name: Fiend's Hand
desc: Arms that reach out from the Swamp of Chaos to drag down the damned.

name: Fire Eye
desc: An eye engulfed in flames that flaps its wings to create hot blasts of air.

name: Fire Kraken
desc: A squid that thrives on fire and heat.

name: Fire Reaper
desc: A reaper with a flaming arrow that burns an enemy to a crisp.

name: Firegrass
desc: A fire-breathing plant found growing near volcanoes.

name: Firewing Pegasus
desc: A heavenly stallion soaring through the skies on crimson wings.

name: Fireyarou
desc: A malevolent creature wrapped in flames that attacks enemies with intense fire.

name: Flame Cerebrus
desc: Known to many as the "Burning Executioner", this monster is capable of burning enemies to cinders.

name: Flame Champion
desc: A warrior protected by a flaming shield that nullifies any attack.

name: Flame Dancer
desc: This monster moves while swinging its burning rope.

name: Flame Manipulator
desc: This Spellcaster attacks enemies with fire-related spells such as "Sea of Flames" and "Wall of Fire".

name: Flame Viper
desc: A fire-breathing snake whose speed makes it a difficult target.

name: Flying Fish
desc: Three wishes are granted to those fortunate enough to see this monster in flight.

name: Flying Kamakiri #2
desc: A flying mantis that feeds primarily on insects.

name: Flying Penguin
desc: A very rare penguin that takes to the air with ears shaped like wings.

name: Frenzied Panda
desc: A savage beast that carries a big bamboo stick for beating down its enemies.

name: Frostosaurus
desc: This monster's metabolism enables it to endure long periods of cold, harnessing the power to become a creature of solid ice! Nothing else can withstand such temperatures, especially victims of its glacial rampage.

name: Fungi of the Musk
desc: Melts away anything that dares to stand before it.

name: Gadget Soldier
desc: A rust-free machine warrior born to battle.

name: Gagagigo
desc: This young evildoer used to have an evil heart, but by meeting a special person, he discovered justice.

name: Gaia The Fierce Knight
desc: A knight whose horse travels faster than the wind. His battle-charge is a force to be reckoned with.

name: Gamma the Magnet Warrior
desc: Alpha, Beta, and Gamma meld as one to form a powerful monster.

name: Ganigumo
desc: A crab that binds its enemies with a sticky web and attacks them with its sharp claws.

name: Garnecia Elefantis
desc: A monster so heavy that each step rocks the earth.

name: Garoozis
desc: An axe-swinging beast-warrior with the head of a dragon.

name: Garvas
desc: A wicked beast that resembles a winged lion.

name: Gate Deeg
desc: This weird monster has a portal in its belly that brings reinforcements from the farthest reaches of the netherworld.

name: Gatekeeper
desc: An indestructible mechanoid created for the sole purpose of guarding the gateways.

name: Gazelle the King of Mythical Beasts
desc:
This monster moves so fast that it looks like an illusion to mortal eyes.


(This card is always treated as a "Phantom Beast" card.)

name: Gem-Knight Crystal
desc: A Gem-Knight officer of high rank, who has optimized the use of the crystal powers. Despite his ability to overwhelm most opponents, he's wary of stretching himself too thin, and opts for solidarity with his comrades.

name: Gem-Knight Garnet
desc: The Gem-Knight Warrior who carries the Garnet Soul. His Flaming Iron Fist crushes all enemies.

name: Gem-Knight Lapis
desc: The best of friends with Lazuli, this soldier deeply cares about the well-being of her friends.

name: Gem-Knight Sapphire
desc: His Sapphire power commands the waters to protect him from attack. His comrades trust in his silent protection.

name: Gem-Knight Tourmaline
desc: He channels mystic energies and changes them into fighting strength through the power of Tourmaline. Many admire his way of life.

name: Gemini Elf
desc: Elf twins that alternate their attacks.

name: Gene-Warped Warwolf
desc: This warwolf was given incalculable strength through horrific genetic manipulation. Its gentle nature was completely wiped out, and it now lives only to unleash destruction.

name: Genin
desc: A creature that defeats its enemies using sleight-of-hand.

name: Ghoul with an Appetite
desc: A monster with a heavy appetite that has never been satisfied.

name: Giant Flea
desc: A massive flea that feeds on the blood of its enemies.

name: Giant Mech-Soldier
desc: This monster swings an earth-shaking axe that cannot be blocked by a common sword.

name: Giant Red Seasnake
desc: A sea-dwelling snake that attacks passing enemies with its sharp teeth.

name: Giant Scorpion of the Tundra
desc: An extraordinary blue scorpion found in the tundra, not in the desert.

name: Giant Soldier of Stone
desc: A giant warrior made of stone. A punch from this creature has earth-shaking results.

name: Giant Turtle Who Feeds on Flames
desc: A crimson-shelled tortoise that feeds on flames.

name: Giga Gagagigo
desc: In order to fight tremendous evil, he gained formidable power through body reconstruction, but lost his heart and his redemption.

name: Giga-Tech Wolf
desc: An iron wolf with razor-sharp fangs that can penetrate any armor.

name: Giganto
desc: A massive steel ball that mows down anything in its path.

name: Gigobyte
desc: He has a tranquil soul, but carries a destiny that one day his heart shall be tainted by evil....

name: Gil Garth
desc: This steel-armored terror machine ruthlessly strikes down enemies with its giant katana.

name: Girochin Kuwagata
desc: Despite its small size, this monster has powerful jaws that can rip metal to shreds.

name: Gladiator Beast Andal
desc: This one-eyed warrior bear is an aggressive hunter that strikes down its prey with the powerful swipes of its claws. No one can bear the brunt of his tremendously fast and heavy blows.

name: Goblin Calligrapher
desc: A Goblin who devotes himself to mastering perfect calligraphy of the word "False". He gives his all to each stroke.

name: Gogiga Gagagigo
desc: His soul long-since collapsed, his body recklessly continues onward, driven by a lust for more power. He no longer resembles his former self....

name: Gokibore
desc: A large, spherical roach that attacks its enemies by rolling over them.

name: Golgoil
desc: An iron giant that appears from a dimensional rift.

name: Gorgon Egg
desc: The gorgon egg's massive eyes are said to reflect the fate of its enemies.

name: Gradius
desc: A high-performance jet fighter with power capsules for variable attack capabilities.

name: Grand Tiki Elder
desc: A masked monster that wields the most deadly of curses.

name: Grappler
desc: A devious snake with a thick body that wraps around an enemy monster and squeezes the life out of it.

name: Graveyard and the Hand of Invitation
desc: A graveyard that serves as a power source for zombies.

name: Great Angus
desc: A very violent beast, it is always berserk. People say that they have never seen it silent.

name: Great Bill
desc: Nothing escapes from this beast's massive mouth.

name: Great White
desc: A giant white shark with razor-sharp teeth.

name: Green Phantom King
desc: This youthful king of the forests lives in a green world, abundant with trees and wildlife.

name: Griffore
desc: This monster's tough hide deflects almost any attack.

name: Ground Attacker Bugroth
desc: A surface battle robot that was once used for sea warfare.

name: Gruesome Goo
desc: A slime boss that is definitely tougher than it looks.

name: Guardian of the Labyrinth
desc: A monster that guards the entrance to the Netherworld.

name: Guardian of the Throne Room
desc: A robot guard built to protect throne rooms, it is armed with homing missiles.

name: Gunkan Suship Shari
desc: ''Finally got to visit that harbor specializing in Gunkan Suships that I've been curious about for a while! The premium "Shari" here is limited to 2000 Suships a year, and uses specially developed smooth aged rice, giving it extra boldness not found anywhere else. The classy atmosphere made my heart sing, too. The Gunkan Suship served had a perfect balance of vinegar, nigiri, shine, and shape, demonstrating exquisite artisanship. The owner told me, "We are introducing rich yet mellow scented EDO-FRONT red vinegar in the near future," which I'm really looking forward to. However, I was disappointed the surrounding seas were a little noisy... so, giving it 4 stars with hope for improvements in the future.''

name: Gyakutenno Megami
desc: This fairy uses her mystical power to protect the weak and provide spiritual support.

name: Haniwa
desc: An earthen figure that protects the tomb of an ancient ruler.

name: Happy Lover
desc: Enemies become overjoyed when struck by the Heart Ray emitted from the forehead of this tiny cherub.

name: Hard Armor
desc: A living suit of armor that attacks enemies with a bone-jarring tackle.

name: Harpie Girl
desc: A Harpie chick who aspires to flit about beautifully and gorgeously, but attack sharply.

name: Harpie Lady
desc: This human-shaped animal with wings is beautiful to watch but deadly in battle.

name: Headless Knight
desc: A haunted spirit of a falsely accused knight who wanders in search of truth and justice.

name: Hercules Beetle
desc: A massive beetle with a tough carapace and a dangerous horn.

name: Hero of the East
desc: Feel da strength ah dis sword-swingin' samurai from da Far East.

name: Hibikime
desc: Confuses enemy monsters with a noise that is harsh to the ears.

name: Hieratic Seal of the Sun Dragon Overlord
desc: A mysterious engraved Hieratic relic. It was thought to be a simple stone, but it was actually infused with the power of a sun-wielding dragon. Aeons passed, and the power of the relic grew and grew until it finally shone like the sun itself.

name: High Tide Gyojin
desc: A very agile half-fish warrior known for its relentless attacks.

name: Hinotama Soul
desc: An intensely hot flame creature that rams anything standing in its way.

name: Hitodenchak
desc: A rabid starfish that spits a lethal acid that can melt almost anything.

name: Hitotsu-Me Giant
desc: A one-eyed behemoth with thick, powerful arms made for delivering punishing blows.

name: Holograh
desc: This machine generates illusions that leave an enemy wide open to attacks.

name: Horn Imp
desc: A small fiend that dwells in the dark, its single horn makes it a formidable opponent.

name: Hourglass of Life
desc: This creature grants power instead of shortening life.

name: Humanoid Slime
desc: This slime apparently has some human genes in its genetic makeup.

name: Hunter Dragon
desc: This dragon has taken down countless prey with its sharp fangs. It strikes very quickly, because if it does not strike first it is vulnerable to a counter-attack.

name: Hunter Spider
desc: This monster feeds on whatever it catches in its web.

name: Hurricail
desc: A tornado that ravages the wastelands with sharp winds that can cut to the bone.

name: Hyo
desc: None can survive the cold touch of this sub-zero warrior.

name: Hyosube
desc: This amphibian is strong on the attack, but leaves much to be desired when defending.

name: Hyozanryu
desc: A dragon created from a massive diamond that sparkles with blinding light.

name: Ice Water
desc: A very aggressive mermaid that attacks enemies with the spikes growing from its body.

name: Ignihorse Dragonith
desc: ''A draco-horse racing around freely upon the boiling sea. It continues to run on the water surface today in order to prevent its own flames from extinguishing. It dreams of one day setting foot upon its homeland.''

name: Ill Witch
desc: This monster blasts enemies with unexpected bursts of wind.

name: Illusionist Faceless Mage
desc: Manipulates enemy attacks with the power of illusion.

name: Inpachi
desc: A log that attacks lost travelers in the forest. Originally a big tree, it was cut down and possessed by a wicked spirit.

name: Insect Knight
desc: Of all Insect fighters, he is the paragon of the Indestructible Insect Invaders, which only the elite of the elite can join. We can no longer ignore their unmatched battle prowess.

name: Invader from Another Dimension
desc: An extraterrestrial monster that came from a distant galaxy.

name: Island Turtle
desc: A huge turtle that is often mistaken for an island.

name: Jack's Knight
desc: A strong master swordsman. His loyalty is to justice, his duty to protect the weak.

name: Jellyfish
desc: An almost invisible, semi-transparent jellyfish that drifts in the sea.

name: Jerry Beans Man
desc: Jerry, a bean soldier, believes he is the strongest warrior in the world, but his true abilities are still untested.

name: Job-Change Mirror
desc: A wicked mirror that blocks off the damaging effects of an attack.

name: Jongleur-Ghoul Illusionist
desc: ''A captivating street performer, who'll catch you off guard with his song and dance and hocus pocus attacks. Once his eyes start spinning, danger is impending, so make a run for it!''

name: Judge Man
desc: This club-wielding warrior battles to the end and will never surrender.

name: Kabazauls
desc: A huge monster in the shape of a hippopotamus. The sneezing from his gigantic body is so fierce that people mistake it for a hurricane.

name: Kagemusha of the Blue Flame
desc: Serving as a double for the Ruler of the Blue Flame, he's a master swordsman that wields a fine blade.

name: Kageningen
desc: He yoozes both a physical and a shadow form ta attack. So he's a tough monstah ta beat!

name: Kairyu-Shin
desc: A sea dragon known as the King of the Ocean, it attacks its enemies with huge tidal waves.

name: Kamakiriman
desc: A man-shaped mantis with two razor-sharp scythes.

name: Kanan the Swordmistress
desc: A lady warrior armed with sword and shield, she floats lightly and stings sharply.

name: Kanikabuto
desc: A monster crab with huge claws for clipping enemies to little pieces.

name: Kappa Avenger
desc: An amphibian that sold his soul for unlimited power to avenge his late friend.

name: Kattapillar
desc: Attacks enemies by spitting thin, sticky webs.

name: Key Mace
desc: Enemies' hearts will melt at the sight of this small fairy's cuteness.

name: Key Mace #2
desc: This fiend brings out the worst in everyone.

name: Killer Needle
desc: A huge bee with exceptional strength that's particularly dangerous in a swarm.

name: King Fog
desc: A fiend that dwells in a blinding curtain of smoke.

name: King of Yamimakai
desc: Wields the power of darkness to destroy its enemies.

name: Kojikocy
desc: A man-hunter with powerful arms that can crush boulders.

name: Korogashi
desc: A high-powered dung beetle that can roll dung larger than itself. It crushes its foes with its massive ball of dung.

name: Koumori Dragon
desc: A vicious, fire-breathing dragon whose wicked flame corrupts the souls of its victims.

name: Kozaky
desc: A workaholic fiend who devotes everything to his research into the languages of Dark World. His mind has collapsed because of working too hard.

name: Krokodilus
desc: A vicious crocodile with great intelligence.

name: Kumootoko
desc: A massive, intelligent spider that traps enemies with webbing.

name: Kurama
desc: A vicious bird that attacks from the skies with its whip-like tail.

name: Kuwagata
desc: A very vicious stag beetle that goes for the head.

name: La Jinn the Mystical Genie of the Lamp
desc: A genie of the lamp that is at the beck and call of its master.

name: Labyrinth Wall
desc: These walls form a labyrinth with no exit for enemies.

name: Lady of Faith
desc: Soothes the souls of others by chanting a mysterious spell.

name: LaLa Li-oon
desc: ''An electric cloud creature, its acid rain makes it very dangerous.''

name: LaMoon
desc: A sorcerer that draws its power from the lunar landscape.

name: Larvas
desc: A fast-moving, bird-like creature that strangles opposing monsters with its long, thin arms.

name: Laughing Flower
desc: A flower whose laugh can confuse the minds of enemies.

name: Launcher Spider
desc: A mechanical spider with rocket launchers capable of random fire.

name: Left Arm of the Forbidden One
desc: A forbidden left arm sealed by magic. Whosoever breaks this seal will know infinite power.

name: Left Leg of the Forbidden One
desc: A forbidden left leg sealed by magic. Whosoever breaks this seal will know infinite power.

name: Legendary Dueling Field
desc: ''A field of battle for those who believe in the Decks they've built, those who never turn their backs on any foes, those brave enough to fight to the very end and wage rites deciding winners and losers. It is said that when they unite their hearts with the hearts of their cards through bonds and take a step forward by swearing on their pride and souls, they can carve open a road continuing on to the as-of-yet unfinished future.''

name: Leo Wizard
desc: A wizard with a black mantle who is actually a talking lion in disguise.

name: Leogun
desc: Huge monster with a lion's mane similar to the King of Beasts.

name: Leotron
desc: A territorial electronic monster that guards its own domain.

name: Lesser Dragon
desc: A minor dragon incapable of breathing fire.

name: Light Bringer Lucifer
desc: ''I am the ruler of all creation sitting atop the supreme throne... let there be light!''

name: Lightning Conger
desc: This massive eel generates huge charges of electricity and unleashes them as thunderbolts.

name: Liquid Beast
desc: A liquid life form that thrives on water.

name: Lisark
desc: A creature with sapphire eyes that mesmerizes and confuses enemies.

name: Little D
desc: Yo, this tyrannosaurus tot's got a terrible temper.

name: Living Vase
desc: A living vase that bites enemies and blinds them with a blast of pollen from its flower.

name: Lizard Soldier
desc: A beast soldier derived from dragons, it is small for a Dragon-Type. Moving very quickly, this monster is an excellent strategist.

name: Lord of the Lamp
desc: This spirit emerges from the mystic lamp and obeys the wishes of its summoner.

name: Lord of Zemia
desc: A wicked entity that manipulates enemies towards a path of destruction.

name: Lucky Trinket
desc: This creature may look slim and weak, but it's protected by a mystical force.

name: Lunar Queen Elzaim
desc: A lovely creature guarded by the moon. Her lunar curtain can block just about any attack.

name: Luster Dragon
desc: A very beautiful dragon covered with sapphire. It does not like fights, but has incredibly high attack power.

name: Luster Dragon #2
desc: This dragon feeds on emerald. Enchanted by this monster even when attacked, few people live to tell of its beauty.

name: M-Warrior #1
desc: Specializing in combination attacks, this warrior uses magnetism to block an enemy's escape.

name: M-Warrior #2
desc: Specializing in combination attacks, this warrior is equipped with a tough, magnetically coated armor.

name: Mabarrel
desc: This cannon-like creature fires eyeballs so fast they can't be seen.

name: Machine Attacker
desc: This machine, created to lead charges into enemy territory, mows down enemies by rushing.

name: Mad Dog of Darkness
desc: He used to be a normal dog who played around in a park, but was corrupted by the powers of darkness.

name: Mad Lobster
desc: A gourmet food renowned by the Dark World upper crust. It has sensational flavor.

name: Madjinn Gunn
desc: A living weapon that spits projectiles.

name: Magical Ghost
desc: This creature casts a spell of terror and confusion just before attacking its enemies.

name: Maiden of the Moonlight
desc: A sorcerer blessed by lunar light with powers far beyond mortal comprehension.

name: Mammoth Graveyard
desc: A mammoth that protects the graves of its pack and is absolutely merciless when facing grave-robbers.

name: Man Eater
desc: Man-eating plant with poison feelers for attacking enemies.

name: Man-Eating Plant
desc: A meat-eating plant that is attractive to the eye but dangerous when approached.

name: Man-Eating Treasure Chest
desc: A monster disguised as a treasure chest that is known to attack the unwary adventurer.

name: Masaki the Legendary Swordsman
desc: Legendary swordmaster Masaki is a veteran of over 100 battles.

name: Masked Clown
desc: This warrior's fatal dance is performed with a lethal sickle.

name: Master & Expert
desc: A deadly duo consisting of a beast master and its loyal servant.

name: Master Kyonshee
desc: A wandering Kyonshee searching for a strong rival to defeat. They say he was known as the master of all martial arts.

name: Mech Bass
desc: A mechanized bass with a large mouth and a cannon on its back. The cannon fires blinding plasma rays.

name: Mech Mole Zombie
desc: This creature attacks by launching missile-like arms.

name: Mechaleon
desc: A large chameleon with the ability to alter its body coloring. Using this ability, it can conceal itself in any location.

name: Mechanical Snail
desc: A cyborg snail that still travels at a slow pace.

name: Mechanicalchaser
desc: A hunter that relentlessly pursues its target by order of the Machine King.

name: Meda Bat
desc: An eyeball fiend created by a servant of the wicked, it uses "Dark Blasts" to blow away its enemies.

name: Mega Thunderball
desc: Rolls along the ground releasing bolts of electricity to attack its enemies.

name: Megalosmasher X
desc: With its sound-baffling armor and gargantuan jaws, this primeval predator's phosphorescence was the only possible pardon for its primitive prey.

name: Megasonic Eye
desc: Made of mysterious metal, this monster is a doomsday machine from the edge of the universe.

name: Megazowler
desc: Nothing stands in the way of this spike-covered dinosaur!

name: Megirus Light
desc: The fatal beams from the eyes of this monster result in grim destruction.

name: Mekk-Knight Avram
desc: "Check THIS out!"

name: Melchid the Four-Face Beast
desc: This monster has four different masks for four different attacks.

name: Melffy Rabby
desc: ''Rabby's up on that favorite stump again, looking all around the forest at all the fluffy friends! Do you like exploring, too? Good! Let's go find more Melffy friends with Rabby!''

name: Meotoko
desc: Dis big ol' guy wit' a big ol' eye shoots a nasty ray beam right atcha!

name: Metal Armored Bug
desc: A gigantic insect-like creature covered by thick armor. Everything in his path is destroyed.

name: Metal Fish
desc: A metal fish with a razor-sharp caudal fin.

name: Metal Guardian
desc: A fiend guarding the treasures of the netherworld, it's most at home in the dark.

name: Metaphys Armed Dragon
desc: Usually visible despite its phantom existence.

name: Meteor Dragon
desc: This dragon appeared from the sky and crashed to the earth.

name: Midnight Fiend
desc: This monster only appears when a midnight tribute is made.

name: Mighty Guard
desc: A machine soldier that was developed as a guard. It is made of rust-proof metal.

name: Mikazukinoyaiba
desc: A dragon warrior of the moon armed with a crescent sword.

name: Millennium Golem
desc: For nearly a millennium, this golem has served as guardian of an ancient treasure trove.

name: Millennium Shield
desc: A famous shield said to belong to an ancient Egyptian Pharaoh. Legends tell of its power to block any strong attack.

name: Minomushi Warrior
desc: A rock warrior that wields a heavy blade carved from stone.

name: Misairuzame
desc: A missile-launching fish protected by deadly spikes.

name: Mist Valley Watcher
desc: Descendant of a family that has served as Mist Valley watchman over the generations. Never missed a single thing that happened in the valley, no matter how minute.

name: Mokey Mokey
desc: An outcast angel. Nobody knows what he is thinking at all. Sometimes he gets mad and that is dreadful.

name: Molten Behemoth
desc: A giant born from magma, it attacks with a magma punch.

name: Mon Larvas
desc: A further step in the evolutionary chain, it is much more powerful than "Larvas".

name: Monster Egg
desc: A warrior hidden within an egg that attacks enemies by flinging eggshells.

name: Monster Tamer
desc: A master of monsters that exercises control over several creatures.

name: Monstrous Bird
desc: Few have set eyes on this dive-bombing bird and lived to tell the tale.

name: Monsturtle
desc: Protected by a spiked shell, this turtle has a very nasty disposition.

name: Moon Envoy
desc: Many have fallen victim to this lunar warrior's crescent pike.

name: Morinphen
desc: A strange fiend with long arms and razor-sharp talons.

name: Mountain Warrior
desc: A tough warrior that can move smoothly on even the roughest terrain.

name: Mr. Volcano
desc: This seemingly mild-mannered creature has an extremely volatile temper.

name: Muse-A
desc: A fairy of the arts that is unbeatable on the harp.

name: Mushroom Man
desc: Found in humid regions, this creature attacks enemies with a lethal rain of poison spores.

name: Mystery Hand
desc: This monster twists reality and reaches between dimensions to attack its enemies.

name: Mystery Shell Dragon
desc: Mysterious living matter that suddenly appeared from a different dimension. Its attack paralyzes the target's nerves, and causes intense hallucinations.

name: Mystic Clown
desc: Nothing can stop the mad attack of this powerful creature.

name: Mystic Horseman
desc: Half man and half horse, this monster is known for its extreme speed.

name: Mystical Capture Chain
desc: A mystical chain that binds enemies, rendering them immobile.

name: Mystical Elf
desc: A delicate elf that lacks offense, but has a terrific defense backed by mystical power.

name: Mystical Sheep #2
desc: A monstrous sheep with a long tail for hypnotizing enemies.

name: Mystical Shine Ball
desc: A soul of light covered by mystical shine. When you see its beautiful shape, your dream will come true.

name: Neck Hunter
desc: A fiend that wields a mean sickle and fires devastating beams from its eyes.

name: Necrolancer the Time-lord
desc: The one-eyed Necrolancer launches his onslaught from a dimensional ring that can appear out of thin air.

name: Nekogal #1
desc: A pussycat-fairy. Contrary to her lovely beauty, she claws on her enemies.

name: Nekogal #2
desc: A fast and lethal creature with very dangerous claws.

name: Nemuriko
desc: A child-like creature that controls a sleep fiend to beckon enemies into eternal slumber.

name: Neo Aqua Madoor
desc: The true nature of this wizard, who rules all water. It defends itself with a vast, impenetrable wall of ice.

name: Neo Bug
desc: A huge bug-like monster said to come from another planet. It gathers in swarms.

name: Neo the Magic Swordsman
desc: A dimensional drifter who not only practices sorcery, but is also a sword and martial arts master.

name: Night Lizard
desc: A lizard warrior protected by a hide of very tough emerald scales.

name: Nightmare Scorpion
desc: A creature that generates nightmares to haunt an opponent, it attacks with four poisonous tails.

name: Nin-Ken Dog
desc: A Ninja dog who has mastered extreme Ninjutsu. Through hard training, it learned the technique to metamorphose into a human being.

name: Niwatori
desc: Swallows enemies whole and uses their essence as energy.

name: Noble Knight Artorigus
desc:
No one shall ever know the truth behind
That fateful day. Artorigus went forth
To where the brilliant sword didst lay.
Twas the first of many feats so great,
A legend through and through. We sing of him,
Artorigus, the Noble and the brave.
-From the Tales of the Noble Knights

name: Obese Marmot of Nefariousness
desc: An ill-mannered field varmint that will sink its teeth into anything.

name: Octoberser
desc: With the head of a fish and the legs of an octopus, this strange creature attacks enemies by flinging spears.

name: Ocubeam
desc: Frightening in appearance, this creature uses its large eyes and ears to keep track of any movement.

name: Ogre of the Black Shadow
desc: An ogre possessed by the powers of the dark. Few can withstand its rapid charge.

name: Ojama Black
desc: He's one of the Ojama Trio. It's said that he butts in by any means necessary. It's also said that when the three are together, something happens.

name: Ojama Green
desc: He's one of the Ojama Trio. It's said that he butts in by any means necessary. It's also said that when the three are together, something happens.

name: Ojama Yellow
desc: He's one of the Ojama Trio. It's said that he butts in by any means necessary. It's also said that when the three are together, something happens.

name: One Who Hunts Souls
desc: This dangerous creature brandishes a soul-sucking sword.

name: One-Eyed Shield Dragon
desc: This dragon wears a shield not only for its own protection, but also for ramming its enemies.

name: Oni Tank T-34
desc: An armored tank possessed by a fiend that will pursue enemies until they're crushed.

name: Oppressed People
desc: They are oppressed, but believe they will have their freedom someday.

name: Opticlops
desc: A one-eyed giant that serves the "Dark Ruler Ha Des", it skewers its enemies with its sharp horn, shattering them to pieces.

name: Orion the Battle King
desc: None have lived to tell tales of this powerful battle fairy.

name: Oscillo Hero
desc: A strange warrior from another dimension.

name: Overdrive
desc: An all-terrain armored vehicle armed with a heavy-duty machine gun.

name: Pale Beast
desc: With skin tinged a bluish-white, this strange creature is a fearsome sight to behold.

name: Parrot Dragon
desc: A dragon from the cartoons that's more dangerous than it appears to be.

name: Peacock
desc: A large peacock that launches its feathers in a lethal attack.

name: Pendulum Machine
desc: A horrible torture machine with a large pendulum blade.

name: People Running About
desc: Although they always suffer in silence, they swear an oath to inevitably revolt.

name: Petit Angel
desc: A quick-moving and tiny fairy that's very difficult to hit.

name: Petit Dragon
desc: A very small dragon known for its vicious attacks.

name: Petit Moth
desc: This small but deadly creature is better off avoided.

name: Phantasm Spiral Dragon
desc: A ferocious serpent that was being hunted by Atlanteans. Battle-weary and ragged, it came upon an ancient light, and gained new strength for its battle. With its increased power, it launched an invasion of enemy territory with a renewed assault.

name: Phantom Dewan
desc: A sorcerer that can paralyze an enemy with a single curse.

name: Phantom Ghost
desc: A vengeful spirit made up of many restless souls.

name: Phantom Gryphon
desc: A legendary monster that dwells secretly in the mountains, fighting with the harpies over hunting grounds. A single wingbeat is said to cause the fiercest of storms.

name: Pharaoh's Servant
desc: An apparition of those said to formerly serve the Pharaoh. It has tremendous loyalty that does not waiver.

name: Pharaonic Protector
desc: The mummy of a soldier that has been guarding the royal family for thousands of years. Even now, its spirit does not allow anybody to trespass.

name: Pot the Trick
desc: A not-so-powerful servant, he is an errand boy of a master sorcerer.

name: Potato & Chips
desc: ''Potato and Chips always get along. They always idle in their room eating potato chips. Consomm punch ones are delicious too. Norishio ones are delicious too. Potato and Chips' delicious life.''

name: Power Pro Knight Sisters
desc:
''The stadium is now open, and our all-star ladies are ready to take you out to the ball game! It's the beginning of a new baseball legend!
Presenting: The three navigators of the Power Pro world! That's Paa-chan on the left, bright, energetic, and (usually) dependable. On the right we've got Waa-chan, calm, earnest, and level-headed (usually...). And Namiki is in charge up front with little Chikuwa in her tote bag, helping us cheer everyone on!''

name: Power Pro Lady Sisters
desc:
''The three Power Pro girls are best friends! And their passion for baseball soars like a home run!
Aoi Hayakawa was the first female player in the league. Her signature pitch is a submariner she calls The Marine Ball!
Mizuki Tachibana is more of a tomboy than her senpai, best known for her Crescent Moon Pitch and her love for the pudding sold down at Pawado!
Hijiri Rokudo is a catcher with a rare gift for baseball! She's been best friends with Mizuki since junior high and her favorite at Pawado is the Kintsuba!''

name: Prevent Rat
desc: This creature is shielded with a tough hide of hair and is excellent at defending itself.

name: Prisman
desc: This crystalline monster focuses light to create a lethal laser.

name: Protector of the Throne
desc: While the king is away, this queen protects his throne with a mighty defense.

name: Protron
desc: Ancestral species found in electronic space. No one knows how much information it holds.

name: PSY-Frame Driver
desc: A Psychic soldier that rides into battle against the Security Forces on currents of lightning, using an autonomic amplifier called "PSY-Frame".

name: Psychic Kappa
desc: An amphibian with a myriad of powers to shield it from enemy attacks.

name: Queen Bird
desc: This monster attacks enemies using its huge beak.

name: Queen of Autumn Leaves
desc: Queen of the Emerald Forest and wife of the Spirit King, she lives surrounded by vivid red leaves.

name: Queen's Knight
desc: This knight catches her opponents off guard, dominating them with swift yet graceful attacks.

name: Rabidragon
desc: It's a snowfield-dwelling, giant-ear-sporting, super-acoustic, snowball-shaped mutant dragon! There's no way anybody can escape.

name: Rainbow Marine Mermaid
desc: A reticent mermaid who appears only on very rare occasions. She emerges only when a large rainbow arches across the sky.

name: Ray & Temperature
desc: The Sun and the North Wind join hands to deliver a devastating combination of heat and gale-force winds.

name: Red Archery Girl
desc: A mermaid archer that hides in a protective shell, waiting for the right moment to strike.

name: Red-Eyes Black Dragon
desc: ''A ferocious dragon with a deadly attack.''

name: Renge, Gatekeeper of Dark World
desc: His renowned athletic physique has made him famous with the populace of Dark World. They call him "Iron Wall Renge" because no one can break through his incredible defenses.

name: Rhaimundos of the Red Sword
desc: Armed with the Sword of Crimson Flames, this warrior can bind a monster with fiery restraints.

name: Right Arm of the Forbidden One
desc: A forbidden right arm sealed by magic. Whosoever breaks this seal will know infinite power.

name: Right Leg of the Forbidden One
desc: A forbidden right leg sealed by magic. Whosoever breaks this seal will know infinite power.

name: Robolady
desc: A warrior fully covered with metal. It upgrades by fusing with "Roboyarou".

name: Robotic Knight
desc: The Commander of Machine-Types, he serves the Machine King. He is famous for the way he controls his troops.

name: Roboyarou
desc: A warrior fully covered with metal. It upgrades by fusing with "Robolady".

name: Rock Ogre Grotto #1
desc: Protected by a solid body of rock, this monster throws a bone-shattering punch.

name: Rock Ogre Grotto #2
desc: A golem formed by boulders, this monster turns its enemies to stone and crushes them to dust.

name: Rock Spirit
desc: A fairy of boulders that looks like an earthenware statue. It is quite strong in terms of both attack and defense.

name: Rogue Doll
desc: A deadly doll gifted with mystical power, it is particularly powerful when attacking against dark forces.

name: Root Water
desc: An amphibian capable of calling up a massive tidal wave from the dark seas to wipe out enemy monsters.

name: Royal Guard
desc: A mechanized soldier created to protect royalty.

name: Rude Kaiser
desc: With an axe in each hand, this monster delivers heavy damage.

name: Ryu-Kishin
desc: A very elusive creature that looks like a harmless statue until it attacks.

name: Ryu-Kishin Powered
desc: A gargoyle enhanced by the powers of darkness. Very sharp talons make it a worthy opponent.

name: Ryu-Ran
desc: A vicious little dragon sheltered in an egg that looks deceptively harmless.

name: Sabersaurus
desc: This normally gentle dinosaur enjoys relaxing in its nest in the prairies. If it becomes angered, it turns terribly ferocious.

name: Saggi the Dark Clown
desc: This clown appears from nowhere and executes very strange moves to avoid enemy attacks.

name: Sand Stone
desc: Appears from underground and attacks with long, snake-like tentacles.

name: Science Soldier
desc: Soldiers equipped with state-of-the-art weaponry to face unknown creatures.

name: Sea Kamen
desc: A merciless monster that tears opponents to shreds with razor-like claws.

name: Sea King Dragon
desc: Protected by a tough shell, this master of the sea attacks its enemies with toxic bubbles.

name: Sea Serpent Warrior of Darkness
desc: A warrior who defends the world of the Sea of Darkness. He prides himself on his fighting prowess both on the ground and, of course, in the water.

name: Sealmaster Meisei
desc: One of the few people who has a good command of Talismans. His history is a mystery.

name: Sectarian of Secrets
desc: This wizard worships the darkness, and is served by a sinister hand that drags its enemies into oblivion.

name: Seiyaryu
desc: A mystical dragon that burns away the unworthy with its mystic flames.

name: Sengenjin
desc: An unstoppable savage that carries Millennium Items.

name: Sentinel of the Seas
desc: A merman warrior that relentlessly attacks those who pollute the seas with their presence.

name: Serpent Marauder
desc: A snake with a single eye that blows an icy breath to freeze its opponents.

name: Serpent Night Dragon
desc: A dragon created from the soul of a wicked knight.

name: Shadow Specter
desc: Powerful in groups, this animal spirit can be found in the wastelands.

name: Shapesnatch
desc: A bow tie with horrible power, it attacks an opponent by controlling others.

name: Shining Abyss
desc: This monster employs the powers of both Light and Darkness.

name: Shining Friendship
desc: The peacemaker among monsters.

name: Shiny Black "C" Squadder
desc: ''Wherever there are shadows, you'll find the "C" Squad! Their hidden flying abilities let them confront the giants on equal terms!''

name: Shovel Crusher
desc: Armed with a pair of shovels, this monster will destroy anything that stands in its way.

name: Silver Fang
desc: A snow wolf that's beautiful to the eye, but absolutely vicious in battle.

name: Skull Dog Marron
desc: A lost dog that wandered off 1000 years ago. He's still waiting for his master to come for him.

name: Skull Mariner
desc: A pirate ship that appears out of the mist and sinks any seagoing vessels.

name: Skull Red Bird
desc: This monster swoops down and attacks with a rain of knives stored in its wings.

name: Skull Servant
desc: A skeletal ghost that isn't strong but can mean trouble in large numbers.

name: Skull Stalker
desc: Foist he's gonna grab yer monstah wit' his claws, den attack again wit' his poizin stingah!

name: Sky Dragon
desc: A flying dragon with four wings housing some very dangerous blades.

name: Sky Scout
desc: With eyes like a hawk and a flying speed exceeding Mach 5, this monster is a master of the sky.

name: Sleeping Lion
desc: A ferocious animal that sleeps all day. Sometimes it's better to let Sleeping Lions lie.

name: Slime Toad
desc: A slime with the head of a frog, it attacks by croaking terribly.

name: Slot Machine
desc: The machine's ability is said to vary according to its slot results.

name: Snakeyashi
desc: This monster is formed by several serpents that break off to individually attack nearby enemies.

name: Soitsu
desc: Apparently totally unreliable, he wonders if he has incredible potential.

name: Solitude
desc: This beast-warrior swings a massive scythe that feeds on the souls of the slain.

name: Sonic Duck
desc: A duck which can walk at a sonic speed. Sometimes, he cannot deal with his incredible pace and loses control.

name: Sonic Maid
desc: A maiden that uses sound to her advantage, she wields a scythe that's shaped like a musical note.

name: Sorcerer of the Doomed
desc: A slave of the dark arts, this sorcerer is a master of life-extinguishing spells.

name: Soul Tiger
desc: The soul of a tiger that is said to devour human souls. He is a famous soul that you wouldn't want to run into in a dark alley.

name: Souleater
desc: A living wonder of mystery.

name: Souls of the Forgotten
desc: A wicked spirit created by the hateful souls of those who fell in battle. It grows by assimilating the souls of its enemies.

name: Space Mambo
desc: A Space Mambo floating in the vast universe. This living relic was found in the ruins of a super civilization on Alphard 4.

name: Spherous Lady
desc: Many have been deceived by the beauty of this vampire.

name: Spike Seadra
desc: Using the spikes sprouting from its body, this creature stabs its opponents and floods them with electricity.

name: Spikebot
desc: A mechanical soldier created by a wicked sorcerer, it attacks with the two steel balls attached to its arms.

name: Spiked Snail
desc: A very fast, bipedal snail with a pair of lethal arms.

name: Spiral Serpent
desc: When huge whirlpools lay cities asunder, it is the hunger of this sea serpent at work. No one has ever escaped its dreaded Spiral Wave to accurately describe the terror they experienced.

name: Spirit of the Books
desc: This wise spirit dwells in books, using its accumulated knowledge to defeat enemies.

name: Spirit of the Harp
desc: A spirit that soothes the soul with the music of its heavenly harp.

name: Spirit of the Mountain
desc: An elderly magician that raises mountains with his flute.

name: Spirit of the Winds
desc: A free-spirited wind elemental that flits about as it desires. It brings storms when it becomes upset.

name: Steam Knight - Hamburk
desc: ''One of the knights, he is equipped with "BFS Armor", which is made of a dense steel carefully refined at the factory, and "Foil-Packer", a special mechanism that can be converted into various weapons depending on the state of combat, thanks to it being linked with the highly analytical "Coc-OS". Although "Hamburk" is equipped with the usual suite of equipment, he is incredibly popular thanks to his combat style being extremely high calorie. His power is further enhanced by the blessings of the goddess "Madera".''

name: Steel Ogre Grotto #1
desc: A steel idol worshipped in the Land of Machines.

name: Steel Ogre Grotto #2
desc: A mechanized iron doll with tremendous strength.

name: Stone Armadiller
desc: Dis stone crittah's got rock-hahd fur. Dat gives him some really good dee-fense!

name: Stone Dragon
desc: A dragon formed by huge boulders that are also used to attack the enemy.

name: Stone Ghost
desc: With a head that erupts when angered, this monster launches a dangerous shower of boulders.

name: Stone Ogre Grotto
desc: A behemoth shaped by giant boulders.

name: Stuffed Animal
desc: It may look like a harmless stuffed animal, but its zipper mouth deals a deadly bite.

name: Succubus Knight
desc: A warrior wizard adept in casting bone-chilling spells.

name: Summoned Skull
desc:
A fiend with dark powers for confusing the enemy. Among the Fiend-Type monsters, this monster boasts considerable force.

(This card is always treated as an "Archfiend" card.)

name: Sunseed Genius Loci
desc: ''This seed can only be harvested from the sacred tree once every thousand years, and will become the guardian spirit of its land after a thousand more.''

name: Supporter in the Shadows
desc: A cute little elf that hides in the shadows and provides spiritual support.

name: Suppression Collider
desc: ''All data crushed by this network warrior's hammer is irretrievably compressed.''

name: Sword Arm of Dragon
desc: This Jurassic juggernaut has a spine covered in sword-like plates, and a tail to split open skulls.

name: Sword Slasher
desc: A lethal engine of destruction that wields two well-honed blades.

name: Swordsman of Landstar
desc: An amateur with a sword, this fairy warrior relies on its mysterious powers.

name: Swordstalker
desc: A monster formed by the vengeful souls of those who passed away in battle.

name: Synchar
desc: This two-headed creature spits laser blasts at its enemies.

name: Takriminos
desc: A member of a race of sea serpents that freely travels through the sea.

name: Takuhee
desc: This bird is known far and wide as a harbinger of doom.

name: Tao the Chanter
desc: Master of Yin and Yang, this wizard handles a delicate balance of spells and counter spells.

name: Tatsunootoshigo
desc: A bizarre monster with the torso of a horse and a fish's tail. It gallops through the sea as if it were the wind.

name: Temple of Skulls
desc: A mysterious temple of skulls and bones that pulls in unsuspecting enemies.

name: Tenderness
desc: An adorable fairy that celebrates the gift of love.

name: Tentacle Plant
desc: A carnivorous plant that has an outgrowth of tentacles. It attacks someone nearby by extending its tentacles.

name: Terra the Terrible
desc: Known as a swamp dweller, this creature is a minion of the dark forces.

name: Terrorking Salmon
desc: A feared salmon, master of the Sea of Darkness. Its roe is the best delicacy in the World of Darkness.

name: That Which Feeds on Life
desc: A monster that feeds on the energy of other creatures.

name: The 13th Grave
desc: A zombie that suddenly appeared from plot #13 - an empty grave.

name: The All-Seeing White Tiger
desc: A proud ruler of the jungle that some fear and others respect.

name: The Bewitching Phantom Thief
desc: An elegant thief with a black cloak that charms its enemies.

name: The Dragon Dwelling in the Cave
desc: A huge dragon dwelling in a cave. It is horrible when it gets angry, although it is usually quiet. It is said to preserve certain treasures.

name: The Drdek
desc: A bipedal eyeball that seldom misses an enemy with its lethal talons.

name: The Earl of Demise
desc: This gentlemanly creature is extremely wicked, feared by man and fiend alike.

name: The Furious Sea King
desc: Grand King of the Seven Seas, he's able to summon massive tidal waves to drown the enemy.

name: The Gross Ghost of Fled Dreams
desc: This monster feeds on the dreams of an unwary sleeper, dragging the victim into eternal slumber.

name: The Illusory Gentleman
desc: Wearing odd fashions, this gentleman is very fickle. He sometimes saves people and at other times commits crimes.

name: The Judgement Hand
desc: An all-powerful hand that delivers ruthless attacks.

name: The Melting Red Shadow
desc: This monster melts away to materialize under its enemies, taking them by surprise.

name: The Portrait's Secret
desc: A portrait cursed by the artist, it is said to bring ill fortune to anyone who owns it.

name: The Shadow Who Controls the Dark
desc: A shadow that dwells in the dark, paralyzing its opponents and rendering them harmless.

name: The Snake Hair
desc: A monster with a head of poison snakes. One look from this monster can turn an opponent to stone.

name: The Statue of Easter Island
desc: A stone monument from Easter Island that launches laser blasts from its rock-hewn lips.

name: The Thing That Hides in the Mud
desc: This monster melts its way underground to attack enemies from below.

name: The Wandering Doomed
desc: A monster that wanders the edges of the netherworld.

name: Thousand-Eyes Idol
desc: A wicked entity that controls the hearts of men, its thousand eyes are able to see and expand the negative influences in an individual's soul.

name: Three-Headed Geedo
desc: A three-headed nocturnal monster that is absolutely ruthless when fighting.

name: Three-Legged Zombies
desc: A pair of friendly skeletons, lean and fat, that travel with extreme difficulty.

name: Thunder Kid
desc: This monster stores electricity within his body, and can unleash it with catastrophic power.

name: Tiger Axe
desc: A fast and powerful axe-wielding beast-warrior.

name: Toad Master
desc: A hermit frog that has been in existence for thousands of years, it attacks with tadpoles.

name: Togex
desc: An agile monster that rolls up to ram its opponents.

name: Tomozaurus
desc: Small but vicious, this monster even attacks its own kind.

name: Tongyo
desc: This monster captures other fish with its long tongue and sucks the energy out of them.

name: Toon Alligator
desc: An alligator monster straight from the cartoons.

name: Torike
desc: Although a poor defender, this monster's sharp horn gives it an edge when attacking.

name: Trakodon
desc: A tiger-striped dragon that is often seen racing across the wasteland at tremendous speeds.

name: Trance the Magic Swordsman
desc: A peculiar magician with considerable abilities. Supposedly, he's just returned from a trip to outer space.

name: Trent
desc: A guardian of the woods, this massive tree is believed to be immortal.

name: Tri-Horned Dragon
desc: An unworthy dragon with three sharp horns sprouting from its head.

name: Trial of Nightmare
desc: This fiend passes judgment on enemies that are locked in coffins.

name: Tripwire Beast
desc: This creature attacks with electromagnetic waves.

name: Turtle Bird
desc: An unusual turtle that not only swims at tremendous speeds, but can also sail across the skies.

name: Turtle Raccoon
desc: A cunning raccoon protected by a solid turtle shell, it attacks with deception.

name: Turtle Tiger
desc: A tiger encased in a protective shell that attacks with razor-sharp fangs.

name: Turu-Purun
desc: A strange, one-eyed monster that can fell an enemy with a single stab of its spear.

name: Twin Long Rods #1
desc: With whip-like arms, this creature can attack enemies from a distance.

name: Twin Long Rods #2
desc: An amphibious creature with two whip-like tails.

name: Twin-Headed Fire Dragon
desc: Two dragons fused as one from the effects of the Big Bang.

name: Two-Headed King Rex
desc: A powerful monster whose two heads attack as one.

name: Two-Mouth Darkruler
desc: A dinosaur with two deadly jaws, it stores electricity in its horn and releases high voltage bolts from the mouth on its back.

name: Tyhone
desc: Capable of firing cannonballs from its mouth for long-range attacks, this creature is particularly effective in mountain battles.

name: Tyhone #2
desc: A crimson dragon that spits fireballs to create a blazing sea of fire.

name: Unicycular
desc: The third of the brothers, following Tricular and Bicular.

name: United Resistance
desc: The people that gather to swear to fight their oppressors. A revolution is coming.

name: Unknown Warrior of Fiend
desc: The speed of this warrior creates an intense vacuum that can slice through a monster's hide.

name: Uraby
desc: Fast on its feet, this dinosaur rips enemies to shreds with its sharp claws.

name: Ushi Oni
desc: A bull fiend restored by the dark arts, this monster appears out of a jar.

name: V-Tiger Jet
desc: This ace fighter is unbeatable in a dogfight. It combines with other monsters to launch an array of encircling attacks.

name: Venom Cobra
desc: Hard scales cover all parts of this gigantic cobra. It hunts by shooting out massive amounts of venom, but because of its large size, its attack pattern is easily predicted.

name: Violent Rain
desc: This monster can call forth sudden torrents of battering rain.

name: Vishwar Randi
desc: This lady warrior with unquenchable bloodlust serves the forces of darkness.

name: Volcanic Rat
desc: This mutated mouse dwells in the core of active volcanoes. No amount of heat is too much for it to bear.

name: Vorse Raider
desc: This wicked Beast-Warrior does every horrid thing imaginable, and loves it! His axe bears the marks of his countless victims.

name: Warrior Dai Grepher
desc: The warrior who can manipulate dragons. Nobody knows his mysterious past.

name: Warrior of Zera
desc: A wandering warrior who seeks the sanctuary where he can gain the power of the Archlords. To escape the temptation of evil fiends, he fights solo day by day.

name: Water Element
desc: A sea-dwelling spirit that takes away sight by clouding the area in fog.

name: Water Girl
desc: A lovely lady who can launch water projectiles that turn into lethal ice spikes before they reach an opponent.

name: Water Magician
desc: This monster swamps an opponent with an almost endless supply of water.

name: Water Omotics
desc: Transforms the water overflowing from a jar into attacking dragons.

name: Waterdragon Fairy
desc: A water fairy that is said to be able to summon a giant sea serpent.

name: Wattaildragon
desc:
Capable of indefinite flight. Attacks by wrapping its body with electricity and ramming into opponents.
IMPORTANT: Capturing the "Wattaildragon" is forbidden by the Ancient Rules and is a Level 6 offense, the minimum sentence for which is imprisonment for no less than 2500 heliocycles.

name: Wattkid
desc: A creature that electrocutes opponents with bolts of lightning.

name: Weather Control
desc: This creature controls weather and is often the cause of mountain storms.

name: Wetha
desc: A spirit that controls rain and is capable of summoning hurricanes to blow the enemy away.

name: Whiptail Crow
desc: Attacks from the skies with a whip-like tail.

name: White Dolphin
desc: A white dolphin with a horn that summons huge tidal waves.

name: White Duston
desc: The proudust of them all.

name: Wicked Dragon with the Ersatz Head
desc: A two-headed dragon with a pair of jaws that can tear an enemy to shreds.

name: Wilmee
desc: A rabid rabbit that shears through opposition with its sharp skewers.

name: Wing Eagle
desc: This flying creature never misses its intended target.

name: Wing Egg Elf
desc: This fairy in an eggshell uses massive wings to blow back almost any projectile attack.

name: Winged Cleaver
desc: Few can withstand the scythe-like arms of this dangerous creature.

name: Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress #1

name: Winged Dragon, Guardian of the Fortress #2
desc: This monster's wings are capable of generating tornadoes.

name: Winged Egg of New Life
desc: Legend has it that this creature can foretell the birth of children.

name: Wings of Wicked Flame
desc: Crimson wings of fire make this a very lethal creature.

name: Wingweaver
desc: A six-winged fairy who prays for peace and hope.

name: Witty Phantom
desc: Dressed in a night-black tuxedo, this creature presides over the darkness.

name: Wolf

name: Wolf Axwielder
desc: Once it has started battle, this monster attacks fiercely and cannot stop.

name: Wood Clown

name: Wood Remains

name: Woodborg Inpachi

name: Worm Drake
desc: Once this monster wraps itself around a victim, there is no escape.

name: Wow Warrior
desc: A fish with arms, legs, and some very sharp teeth.

name: Wretched Ghost of the Attic
desc: A harmless monster found lurking in just about any attic.

name: X-Saber Anu Piranha
desc: A female X-Saber Warrior, known for her graceful attacks and calm decision making in battle. Her ambition is merciless, and strikes fear in the hearts of her enemies.

name: Yaiba Robo
desc: A cubical machine equipped with cutting blades for shredding an opponent to mincemeat.

name: Yamadron

name: Yamatano Dragon Scroll
desc: A dragon conjured from the very scroll in which it was depicted.

name: Yaranzo
desc: A treasure box containing a monster that attacks any unwary bandit.

name: Yashinoki
desc: An intelligent palm tree that drops a hail of rock-hard coconuts on its enemies.

name: Yormungarde
desc: An extremely long snake that dwells in the world of myth.

name: Zanki
desc: His swiftly drawn blade delivers quick and fatal damage.

name: Zarigun
desc: A lethal crawfish with extremely dangerous claws.

name: Zoa
desc: A monster whose full potential can be achieved when outfitted with "Metalmorph".

name: Zombino
desc:
The two are so close
They die and return to life
Inseparable
